<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_104" id="50v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_104_r2l12">Andreſen <expan>Hall<ex>er</ex></expan> / Jacob Toppler / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l13">Caſpar VVernitʒer cʒu <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</del></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_104_r2l15">Lieben frewnde / als Jr vns <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / von der 
<del rend="strikethrough"> habe </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_104_r2l14">varndenhabe vnd brief </ab></add> <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l16">die <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Toppler <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vat<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Sweher <expan>ſelige<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒingell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l17">vnd Stephan Schuler <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> beuolhen hat / das vvir die <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l18">vveiſen vnd heiſʒen <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ ſie euch ſölch habe vnd briefe <expan>gutlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l20">widergeben <expan>ſolte<ex>n</ex></expan> etc 
<add><ab facs="#facs_104_r2l19">daʒ haben wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab></add> laſʒen 
<del rend="strikethrough">vvir </del> euch <expan>wiſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ wir <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l21"><expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> be d </del> durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> beſant vnd ʒu rede geſatʒt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l22">vnd die haben vns <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> das <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Tötter von <expan>Nöꝛdlınge<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l24">dieſelben habe 
<add><ab facs="#facs_104_r2l23">vnd brief </ab></add> bey Jn 
<del rend="strikethrough">verb </del> mit dem <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>pote<ex>n</ex></expan> habe / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l25">nu fuge Jn nicht das ſie die on reht herauſʒ geben / deucht euch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l26">
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſie </del> aber daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſie </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_104_line_1576678827434_12857">Jr </ab></add> darüber ʒu den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ vnſern <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> icht cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l27"> <expan>ſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> het 
<del rend="strikethrough">en </del> / <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> wöllen ſie Jm ~ eins <expan>frewntliche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſein / </ab>
</del>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_104" id="50v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Andresen <expan>Hall<ex>er</ex></expan>, Jacob Toppler
                            und Caspar Werniczer czu <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</del></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Lieben frewnde, als ir uns
                                <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von der <add>varndenhabe und
                                brief</add>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, die <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                            Toppler, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vat<ex>er</ex></expan> und sweher
                            <expan>selige<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan>
                            Czingell und Stephan Schuler, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, bevolhen hat, das wir die
                                    <expan>unt<ex>er</ex></expan> weisen und heiszen
                                    <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz sie euch sölch habe und
                            briefe <expan>gutlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> widergeben
                                    <expan>solte<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <add>Daz haben wir wol
                                        <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und</add> laszen
                            euch <expan>wisze<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> besant und zu rede gesaczt
                                    <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und die haben uns
                                    <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, das
                                <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Tötter von
                                    <expan>Nördlinge<ex>n</ex></expan> dieselben habe <add>und
                                brief</add> bey in mit dem <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>pote<ex>n</ex></expan> habe. Nu fuge in nicht, das
                            sie die on reht herausz geben. Deucht euch aber, daz <add>ir</add>
                            darüber zu den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>, unsern
                                    <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, icht czu
                                    <expan>spreche<ex>n</ex></expan> het,
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> wöllen sie im eins
                                    <expan>frewntliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sein.</del></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
